OL,5, A father-of-three who posted an        
OL,6, "abhorrent" video abusing three England
OL,7, players after the Euro 2020 final has  
OL,8, been handed a suspended sentence.      
OL,10,FBradford Pretty used racist terms to   
OL,11,Frefer to Marcus Rashford, Jadon Sancho 
OL,12,Fand Bukayo Saka in the Facebook clip.  
OL,14,FPretty's solicitor said it was a       
OL,15,F"moment of drunken madness".           
OL,17,FThe 50-year-old plasterer was sentenced
OL,18,Fto 50 days in prison, suspended for 12 
OL,19,Fmonths, at Folkestone Magistrates'     
OL,20,FCourt.                                 
